#   - DRUPAL_VERSION: Version of Drupal to use.
#   - DB_HOST: Hostname for the database container.
#   - DB_NAME: Name of the Drupal database.
#   - DB_USER: Database username.
#   - DB_PASSWORD: Database password.
#   - WEB_PORT: Port to expose the web server.
#
# Notes:
#   - Lines starting with '#' are comments and ignored by Docker.
#   - Do not commit sensitive information (like passwords) to version control.
#   - Update this file to configure your local development environment.
